Presentation :

My bittorrent is a tool aiming at downloadings torrents from the internet.
It can also create and show .torrent files with the right parameters

Usage :

   ./my-bittorent <options> <torrent file>

Options :

   -p : decodes a .torrent file

   -m : creates a .torrent file from single file or folder

   -c : checks the integrity of the downloaded files from a .torrent file

   -d : dunps the peers

How to compile :

   mkdir build && cd build
   cmake ..
   make (or make my-bittorrent)